WEBVTT

1
00:40:03.940 --> 00:40:05.170 
全世界都有他的足迹
He's all over the globe.

2
00:40:05.170 --> 00:40:08.500 
机器人实验室  武器库  喷气动力实验室
Robotics labs, weapons facilities, jet propulsion labs.

3
00:40:08.540 --> 00:40:12.820 
都说有金属人  有时候好多个  过去清空了他们那里
Reports of a metal man, or men, coming in and emptying the place.

4
00:40:12.900 --> 00:40:13.900 
伤亡呢
Fatalities?

5
00:40:13.980 --> 00:40:15.280 
不交火的话没有
Only when engaged.

6
00:40:15.280 --> 00:40:17.050 
他们都变得神情恍惚
Mostly guys left in a fugue state

7
00:40:17.060 --> 00:40:19.510 
说着什么回忆  最深处的恐惧
going on about old memories, worst fears,

8
00:40:19.510 --> 00:40:21.510 
还有东西"快到看不见"
and "something too fast to see."

9
00:40:21.820 --> 00:40:23.020 
马克西莫夫兄妹
Maximoffs.

10
00:40:23.450 --> 00:40:26.140 
难怪他会找他们  他们都认识同一个人
That makes sense he'd go to them. They have someone in common.

11
00:40:26.200 --> 00:40:27.330 
已经不在了
Not anymore.

